## Roadmap

| Version | Watch face features |
|---------|---------------------|
| v6 firmware | One face (Classic). Hand-drawing math working. Raise-to-wake. Tap-to-cycle-info. |
| v7 firmware | Add Sport and Modern faces. App settings to switch faces. |
| v8 firmware | Add Festive (seasonal auto-rotation). |
| v9+ | Art faces (commissioned). User-uploaded backgrounds. |

Each version is a meaningful step. We do not try to ship the whole library at once.

---

## Why this matters

A blood pressure cuff is bought when the user has high blood pressure. A pacemaker is implanted when the user needs a pacemaker. These are *medical objects* — purposeful, but cold.

A wedding ring is worn because of what it means.

We want TIGA to feel closer to the second category. The watch face system is how we get there.

